---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
import Container from "@/components/container.astro";
---

<Layout title="About Us">
  <div class="bg-yellow-600 text-white">
    <Container>
      <div class="py-16 text-center">
        <h1 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">About The Yellow Bait House</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-yellow-200 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          A must-see when visiting Key Largo. More than a bait shop — it's a Keys institution.
        </p>
      </div>
    </Container>
  </div>

  <Container>
    <div class="py-12 lg:py-20">
      <!-- Story -->
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-20">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-yellow-700 mb-6">Our Story</h2>
        <p class="text-stone-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          The Yellow Bait House has been a fixture on US-1 in Key Largo for as long as most
          anglers can remember. That bright yellow building at Mile Marker 101 is the first
          stop for anyone heading out to fish the Upper Keys — and the last stop for anyone
          bringing home dinner.
        </p>
        <p class="text-stone-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          What started as a straightforward bait and tackle shop has grown into something
          bigger: a full seafood market selling only locally caught fish, a rod repair and
          rental shop, a souvenir stop, and now a food menu serving up fresh seafood dishes
          and island-inspired flavors.
        </p>
        <p class="text-stone-600 leading-relaxed">
          But we haven't changed what matters. Our staff still knows every customer by name,
          still gives out free fishing advice, and still treats every kid who walks in like it's
          their first time seeing a live bait tank — because it might be. That's the Yellow
          Bait House way.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Values -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-20">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-5xl mb-4">🏆</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-yellow-700 mb-2">Best in the Upper Keys</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-600">
            137+ reviews and counting. Our customers call us the best bait and tackle in the
            Upper Keys — and the best fish market too.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-5xl mb-4">🤝</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-yellow-700 mb-2">Helpful Staff</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-600">
            Our crew doesn't just sell you bait — they tell you where to fish, what to use,
            and how to catch it. First-timers and pros alike.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-5xl mb-4">🐟</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-yellow-700 mb-2">Local Only</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-600">
            Our seafood market sells exclusively locally caught fish. No imports.
            Best prices in the Keys because we cut out the middleman.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- What We Offer -->
      <div class="bg-yellow-100 rounded-2xl p-8 lg:p-12 mb-20">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-yellow-700 mb-6 text-center">Everything Under One Roof</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          <div class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-2xl shrink-0">🦐</span>
            <p class="text-stone-600">Live bait — shrimp, pilchards, pinfish, mullet, crabs</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-2xl shrink-0">🧊</span>
            <p class="text-stone-600">Frozen bait — ballyhoo, squid, chum blocks</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-2xl shrink-0">🎣</span>
            <p class="text-stone-600">Full tackle shop — hooks, rigs, leader, line, lures</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-2xl shrink-0">🔧</span>
            <p class="text-stone-600">Rod repairs — broken tips, snapped guides, fixed on-site</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-2xl shrink-0">🎣</span>
            <p class="text-stone-600">Rod & reel rentals — fish today, even without gear</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-2xl shrink-0">🦀</span>
            <p class="text-stone-600">Seafood market — stone crab, fresh fish, lobster, shrimp</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-2xl shrink-0">🍽️</span>
            <p class="text-stone-600">Food menu — fish tacos, poke bowls, fresh seafood dishes</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-2xl shrink-0">🎁</span>
            <p class="text-stone-600">Souvenirs & gifts — take a piece of the Keys home</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="text-2xl shrink-0">🧠</span>
            <p class="text-stone-600">Free fishing advice — where to go, what to use, how to catch it</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- CTA -->
      <div class="text-center">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-yellow-800 mb-4">Come See Us</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-stone-600 mb-8 max-w-xl mx-auto">
          Open daily from 6AM. Right on US-1, Mile Marker 101. Can't miss the yellow building.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a href="tel:+13054510921" class="bg-yellow-600 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-bold text-lg hover:bg-yellow-700 transition-colors">
            📞 (305) 451-0921
          </a>
          <a href="/find-us" class="bg-stone-200 text-stone-800 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-bold text-lg hover:bg-stone-300 transition-colors">
            📍 Get Directions
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Container>
</Layout>
